{"tid":1705333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊撚個再做大愛和平撚呢場運動玩完","createTime":"2019-11-11T01:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T01:16:18.000Z","uid":298795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e507268d092b98f308c2308a834f392e7754829","tid":1705333,"uid":298795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:03:28.000Z","msg":"彥霖 周同學 今日兩位手足 仲有好多好多真相未明嘅被自殺兒女<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地幾撚時先會醒？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地知唔知我地對緊啲咩畜生？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢地唔撚會因為你勸交就放低把槍</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[black]<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地根本只係想殺人，就係咁簡單</span>[/black]</span><br />\n以前我都係寧動口不動手嘅淆底獸<br />\n次次都大安旨意要班手足幫你衝<br />\n講左十世嘅全民口罩大罷工都咁兒戲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該你地聽住</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你淆一次底就有手足俾狗殺</strong></span><br />\n香港人幾時先肯爆發大規模反抗？"},{"pid":"e6a0821743ee4652f4fa872be2cce13ba18e94e7","tid":1705333,"uid":298795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲呀屌你老母<br />\n點解次次都要見到有手足受重傷香港人先維持到憤怒值<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77973ad705c39d3b91405ff267399acd6ab0a0ce","tid":1705333,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4cHBEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4cHBEO.jpg&h=aaf225a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有冇人記得10月1<br />\n根本有第一次就會有第二次<br />\n有第二次就會有第三次<br />\n遲早當街當巷殺死人<br />\n啲狗都唔需要負任何責任<br />\n覺得唔關自己事嗰啲人幾時先會醒啊<br />\n仲有落車拆rb屌人阻住你返工嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒阿！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XhAcnH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XhAcnH.png&h=a44173b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oosXqE7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoosXqE7.png&h=48c6159d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7430befd578831e27d4b7c33fec9212b81f620b","tid":1705333,"uid":298795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:09:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我認撚住呢條撚屌</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4MYacN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4MYacN.jpg&h=494f0a71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V36QLL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV36QLL7.jpg&h=41c8694b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5aab0b0081011440db6bb72fe590b96cb5267cc","tid":1705333,"uid":298795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:11:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">返乜撚嘢工啊平行時空撚</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你要死幾多後生仔先肯企出黎</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc32cf6343f1d1606e6bb66a713cd5fb8f88569","tid":1705333,"uid":298795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:12:09.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到文我都要講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c302fb3541f17232ded553ca51ca35d893dc9311","tid":1705333,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"我用最卑微嘅心，求吓咁多位<br />\n<br />\n香港人，忍無可忍！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區